    Infant and Young Children Indicators Dataset

    iycfData.Rd

    This sample demo dataset (`iycfData`) contained 359 observations and 49 variables. The following tables explain the detailed description of each variable included in the sample dataset. The CARE International Myanmar Country program provided this demo dataset, and all the Personal Identifiable Information (PII) were excluded.

    iycfData

    Format

    A data frame with 49 columns and 359 rows.

    **Variables** | **Description** :--- | :--- *csex* | *calc_age_months* | *child_bf* | *child_eibf* | *child_eibf_hrs* | *child_eibf_days* | *chhild_addbf* | *chhild_addbf1* | *chhild_addbf2* | *chhild_addbf3* | *chhild_addbf4* | *chhild_addbf5* | *chhild_addbf888* | *child_bfyest* | *note_liquid* | *note_liquid2* | *child_vitdrop* | *child_ors* | *child_water* | *child_juice* | *child_broth* | *child_porridge* | *child_bms* | *child_bms_freq* | *child_milk* | *child_milk_freq* | *child_mproduct* | *child_mproduct_freq* | *child_liquid* | *note_solid_guide* | *info_solid_food* | *child_rice* | *child_potatoes* | *child_pumpkin* | *child_beans* | *child_leafyveg* | *child_mango* | *child_fruit* | *child_organ* | *child_beef* | *child_fish* | *child_insects* | *child_eggs* | *child_yogurt* | *child_fat* | *child_plam* | *child_sweets* | *child_condiments* | *child_food_freq* |
